    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg style="pūṭṭuvil" xml:id="Aink76">
<l>paiñcāyk kūntaṟ pacumalarc cuṇaṅkiṟ</l>
<l>ṟaṇpuṉa lāṭittaṉ ṉalamēm paṭṭaṉa</l>
<l>ḷoṇṭoṭi maṭavara ṉiṉṉō</l>
<l>ṭantara makaḷirkkut teyvamum pōṉṟē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">


  
<l>   Bathing with you in the cool flood,</l> 
<l> with her beauty spots like green blossoms,  </l> 
<l> and her locks like Paiñcāy grass, </l> 
<l> she rose to the heights of loveliness – </l> 
<l> the simple girl in bright bracelets, </l> 
<l> looking like a goddess, even to celestial women. </l> 


</lg>
